# {{project_name}} Verification Checklist

Use this checklist after generation and after major local edits.

## Baseline

```bash
go test ./...
go run . services
go run . serve --config config/server.dev.yaml
```

## Required HTTP Checks

- `GET /healthz`
- `GET /livez`
- `GET /readyz`
- `GET /startupz`

## Optional Route Checks

- `GET /docs/openapi.yaml` when Swagger is enabled
- `GET /ui` when embedded UI is enabled
- `GET /metrics` on `heavy`

## Business Checks

- Exercise the generated `user` CRUD flow on `medium`, `heavy`, and `light`
- Confirm deleted records return a JSON `404` envelope
- Confirm gzip and ETag behavior on presets that include those middleware defaults

## Environment Checks

- Start once with `config/server.dev.yaml`
- Start once with `config/server.prod.yaml`
- Confirm SQLite and log paths are writable in each target environment
